com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Class Device

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.Device
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDevice
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Beacon, CloudBeacon

    public abstract class Device
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDevice
    Represents device assigned to the Manager.

    By convention this model is fully immutable. To create new instance of the model, please use the Beacon.Builder or CloudBeacon.Builder.
